<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 21:13:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际货币基金组织总裁格奥尔基耶娃表示，中国不能再依赖出口来实现增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imfs-georgieva-says-china-can-no-longer-rely-exports-growth-2024-10-17/</link><description>国际货币基金组织总裁克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃周四对路透社表示，中国体量太大，无法继续依赖出口来推动经济，除非转向消费驱动型经济模式，否则中国将面临危险的增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 21:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/imfs-georgieva-says-china-can-no-longer-rely-exports-growth-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>芬太尼受害者家属要求美国就阿片类药物危机对中国征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/families-fentanyl-victims-ask-us-china-tariffs-over-opioid-crisis-2024-10-17/</link><description>周四，一群亲人死于芬太尼过量的家庭向美国贸易代表戴凯瑟琳·戴 (Katherine Tai) 办公室提交了一份请愿书，要求对中国涉嫌助长美国合成阿片类药物危机的行为进行调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 20:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/families-fentanyl-victims-ask-us-china-tariffs-over-opioid-crisis-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>白宫警告中国利用生产过剩谋求全球主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-says-china-making-far-more-goods-than-it-needs-overtake-global-markets-2024-10-17/</link><description>白宫官员戴利普·辛格(Daleep Singh)周四表示，中国生产的商品远远超过其主导全球市场所需的数量，并补充说，这个亚洲巨人已经积累了不断增长的市场力量，可用于发挥经济和地缘政治影响力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 20:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-says-china-making-far-more-goods-than-it-needs-overtake-global-markets-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国机器人出租车公司小马智行申请赴美IPO</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-robotaxi-firm-pony-ai-files-us-ipo-2024-10-17/</link><description>由汽车制造商丰田支持的中国自动驾驶公司小马智行周四在美国申请首次公开募股，这是投资者对新上市兴趣日益浓厚和监管压力缓解的又一迹象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-robotaxi-firm-pony-ai-files-us-ipo-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士黄金出口因印度供应减少而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/swiss-gold-exports-fall-lower-supplies-india-2024-10-17/</link><description>全球最大的黄金精炼和转运中心周四的海关数据显示，由于对印度的出货量减少，瑞士 9 月份的黄金出口跌至 6 月份以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 16:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/swiss-gold-exports-fall-lower-supplies-india-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国经济放缓，雷朋 (Ray-Ban) 制造商 EssilorLuxottica 销售未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ray-ban-maker-essilorluxottica-misses-sales-expectations-asia-weighs-2024-10-17/</link><description>法意眼镜制造商 EssilorLuxottica 周四第三季度营收未达到预期，因中国消费者支出放缓而受到影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 16:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ray-ban-maker-essilorluxottica-misses-sales-expectations-asia-weighs-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国因在乌克兰使用攻击无人机而对中国和俄罗斯实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/us-sanctions-chinese-russians-over-attack-drones-used-ukraine-2024-10-17/</link><description>美国周四制裁了两家参与制造和运输攻击无人机的中国公司和一家俄罗斯子公司，并警告两国停止推动乌克兰战争的合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 16:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/us-sanctions-chinese-russians-over-attack-drones-used-ukraine-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织总裁预计中期增长温和，敦促改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-chief-expects-lukewarm-growth-medium-term-urges-reforms-2024-10-17/</link><description>国际货币基金组织总裁克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃周四表示，国际货币基金组织的新预测表明，全球经济未来将面临困难，中期增长乏力，贸易紧张局势升级，债务水平高企。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-chief-expects-lukewarm-growth-medium-term-urges-reforms-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>继美洲杯设计之后，氢追逐船也紧随其后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/hydrogen-chase-boats-follow-wake-americas-cup-designs-2024-10-17/</link><description>美洲杯帆船赛期间，在挤满巴塞罗那港口的船只舰队中，有六艘看起来充满未来感的船只在海浪上方静静地进出。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 13:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/hydrogen-chase-boats-follow-wake-americas-cup-designs-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>英国外交大臣将访华重建受损关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-minister-visit-china-rebuild-damaged-ties-2024-10-17/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米将于周五开始对中国进行为期两天的访问，以改善两国因安全问题和涉嫌侵犯人权而紧张多年的关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-foreign-minister-visit-china-rebuild-damaged-ties-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>尽管欧盟关税计划，中国仍欢迎奥地利企业投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-welcomes-austrian-firms-invest-despite-eu-tariffs-plan-2024-10-17/</link><description>商务部声明称，在欧盟计划对中国电动汽车加征关税的情况下，中方希望奥地利企业有信心来华投资、与中方合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 11:29:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-welcomes-austrian-firms-invest-despite-eu-tariffs-plan-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦称美国高关税墙“严重误导”，会抬高物价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-says-high-us-tariff-wall-deeply-misguided-would-raise-prices-2024-10-17/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四表示，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普提议的封锁美国经济的做法将是“严重误导”，这会提高美国消费者的价格，并降低美国企业的竞争力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-says-high-us-tariff-wall-deeply-misguided-would-raise-prices-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：台积电稳定芯片出货，欧洲央行将放松货币政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>德国采取措施加强国内风电产业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/germany-outlines-measures-strengthen-domestic-wind-industry-2024-10-17/</link><description>德国周四表示，正计划为风能生产提供国家担保，作为促进其风能产业一揽子措施的一部分，因为欧洲各国政府和企业对中国企业在该领域的发展势头感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 09:36:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/germany-outlines-measures-strengthen-domestic-wind-industry-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>孟买办事处设立后中方敦促印方慎重处理台湾问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-india-handle-taiwan-issue-cautiously-after-mumbai-office-opening-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国周四敦促印度谨慎处理台湾问题，避免干扰台湾在孟买设立事实上的领事馆后的中印关系改善。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 08:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-india-handle-taiwan-issue-cautiously-after-mumbai-office-opening-2024-10-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>